name: Chelsey Pratt
coverLetter: I haven't trimmed in several years but I can do anything I put my mind to. I'm a single mother an work full time at the Sequoia Humane Society which is a non profit organization so I don't make much. I love my job but was looking to cut a few days off an look for a part time job that pays a little more. I work well with others an would love to be given the opportunity. Thank you so much for your time. Sincerely Chelsey L. Pratt
